<div class="show-container">

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">

      <div class="row product-description">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <%= link_to "Back", products_path, class:"previous" %>
          <%= cl_image_tag @product.photo.key, crop: :fill, class: "product-image" %>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="row justify-content-between">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
              <h5><%= @product.name %></h5>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
              <h5 class=price><%= humanized_money_with_symbol(@product.price) %></h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <%= button_to "Add to cart", {controller: "purchases", action: "create", product_id: params[:id]}, remote: true, id: "buy-button", class: "btn btn-gradient show-button" %>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-check" style="margin-right: 5px;"></i>
            <p><%= @product.deadline.strftime("%d/%m/%Y")  %></p>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf" style="margin-right: 5px;"></i>
            <p style="margin-right: 5px;"><%= @product.CO2e %></p>
            <p> CO2e / kg </p>
          </div>
          <p><%= @product.description %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div style="width: 100%; height: 200px;"
          data-controller="map"
          data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
          data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
      <div class="recipe">
      <p>RECIPE: Apple Pie <i class="fa-solid fa-apple-whole"></i>
          <p></p>
          Peel and core apples, then thinly slice. Preheat the oven to 220 degrees C.
          Melt butter in a saucepan over medium heat. Add flour and stir to form a paste. Add both sugars and water; bring to a boil.
          <p></p>
          Press one pastry into the bottom and up the sides. Roll out remaining pastry. Cut pastry into eight strips.
          Place sliced apples into the bottom crust. Fold the first and third strips all the way back.
          <p></p>
          Repeat Steps 6 and 7.
          Pour sugar-butter mixture over lattice crust, making sure it seeps over sliced apples. Brush some onto lattice, but make sure it doesn't run off the sides.
          Bake in the preheated oven for 35 to 45 minutes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


